&lt;p&gt;Hi, I’m Sun Woo Kim — a PhD student in Computer Science at Simon Fraser University, where I work in the &lt;a href="https://gruvi.cs.sfu.ca/"&gt;GrUVi Lab&lt;/a&gt; under the supervision of &lt;a href="https://xbpeng.github.io/"&gt;Jason Peng&lt;/a&gt;. Before joining SFU, I studied at POSTECH and later earned my master’s degree from Seoul National University under the guidance of &lt;a href="https://mrl.snu.ac.kr/~jehee/"&gt;Professor Jehee Lee&lt;/a&gt;. I’ve also had the chance to collaborate with &lt;a href="https://faculty.cc.gatech.edu/~sha9/"&gt;Professor Sehoon Ha&lt;/a&gt; on projects related to adaptive robot behavior. Most recently, I worked as a researcher at NC AI’s Graphics AI Lab, leading projects on body-gesture generation for virtual agents.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title/><link>https://PulseKim.github.io/image-credit/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://PulseKim.github.io/image-credit/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>